1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:00:06,750 --> 00:00:08,230
She's still her whether in the past or at present.

3
00:00:08,230 --> 00:00:09,480
Do you understand?

4
00:00:09,840 --> 00:00:11,870
Why can she have a fresh start,

5
00:00:12,270 --> 00:00:13,510
but I can't?

6
00:00:16,070 --> 00:00:18,210
You've sent her to a psychiatric hospital?

7
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:20,070
You'd better tell me where she is.

8
00:00:21,110 --> 00:00:22,860
You know what I have on you.

9
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:25,220
Mr. Su.

10
00:00:25,740 --> 00:00:26,830
Where is Ning Mochen?

11
00:00:26,830 --> 00:00:28,070
I'm her husband.

12
00:00:33,270 --> 00:00:34,110
Boss!

13
00:00:35,990 --> 00:00:36,950
What a cute...

14
00:00:36,950 --> 00:00:38,610
Have you finished reading it?

15
00:00:38,790 --> 00:00:39,630
There's no more to it?

16
00:00:39,630 --> 00:00:40,450
No.

17
00:00:40,590 --> 00:00:42,070
This is the whole chapter.

18
00:00:42,230 --> 00:00:43,470
Are you kidding?

19
00:00:43,670 --> 00:00:45,000
You don't get it, right?

20
00:00:45,270 --> 00:00:46,710
Let me explain it to you.

21
00:00:46,910 --> 00:00:49,230
Having characters bounce back from a slump is a strategy.

22
00:00:49,230 --> 00:00:50,690
I've read about the slump.

23
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:51,640
Where's the bounce?

24
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:52,570
The bounce is...

25
00:00:53,990 --> 00:00:54,950
It's...

26
00:00:56,790 --> 00:00:57,790
What a lovely dog!

27
00:00:57,910 --> 00:00:59,710
I'm going to revise the content.

28
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:32,650
[Perfect Her]

29
00:02:33,310 --> 00:02:35,800
[Episode 16]

30
00:02:40,790 --> 00:02:41,550
Dr. Peng,

31
00:02:42,190 --> 00:02:44,150
Conspiring with others to forge medical records

32
00:02:44,150 --> 00:02:45,410
is not only unethical,

33
00:02:45,750 --> 00:02:47,680
but also illegal. Do you know that?

34
00:02:48,430 --> 00:02:51,350
You shouldn't do it even if a patient's father asks you to.

35
00:02:51,350 --> 00:02:53,150
Mr. Su, are you suggesting

36
00:02:54,270 --> 00:02:56,200
that I'm in collusion with Mr. Ning

37
00:02:56,390 --> 00:02:57,550
to jeopardize Ms. Ning?

38
00:02:57,550 --> 00:02:58,630
Isn't it true?

39
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:03,870
Mr. Su,

40
00:03:05,390 --> 00:03:06,270
I understand

41
00:03:06,870 --> 00:03:09,130
that you're protective of your fiancee.

42
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:12,110
But there isn't a problem

43
00:03:13,030 --> 00:03:14,890
with this medical record of hers.

44
00:03:18,950 --> 00:03:19,630
This is

45
00:03:20,530 --> 00:03:22,430
an old medical record of hers.

46
00:03:22,870 --> 00:03:23,910
She was

47
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:26,470
often excited and agitated.

48
00:03:26,829 --> 00:03:27,690
In other words,

49
00:03:28,350 --> 00:03:29,450
she used to be a patient

50
00:03:29,450 --> 00:03:32,220
with typical disruptive mood dysregulation disorder.

51
00:03:32,050 --> 00:03:34,180
[Psychotherapy Notes]

52
00:03:32,990 --> 00:03:35,070
These are the symptoms she developed in childhood.

53
00:03:35,070 --> 00:03:36,490
You can clearly see

54
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:39,650
that she was prone to destructive and abusive behavior.

55
00:03:41,270 --> 00:03:42,100
This one

56
00:03:43,110 --> 00:03:44,910
a recent medical record of hers.

57
00:03:45,510 --> 00:03:46,950
She has repeatedly said

58
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,770
that she is not Ning Mochen.

59
00:03:49,180 --> 00:03:51,770
But when she denies her identity,

60
00:03:52,310 --> 00:03:54,430
she has visual and auditory auditory hallucinations.

61
00:03:53,510 --> 00:03:54,490
[Psychotherapy Notes]

62
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:57,660
She would mistake those for real happenings

63
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:59,750
and gradually develop a condition

64
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:02,480
where delusions and hallucinations both exist.

65
00:04:04,790 --> 00:04:05,630
Mr. Su,

66
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,230
I guess

67
00:04:09,210 --> 00:04:11,120
you have noticed

68
00:04:11,580 --> 00:04:13,910
that she is different from before, right?

69
00:04:15,930 --> 00:04:17,040
Or let's say,

70
00:04:17,670 --> 00:04:20,110
she's different from the old Ning Mochen.

71
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:25,200
Actually, the information I've gathered

72
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:30,070
shows that she has already displayed signs of delusional disorder.

73
00:04:54,980 --> 00:04:59,300
[Refuse] [Answer]

74
00:04:54,980 --> 00:04:59,300
[Ning Mochen]

75
00:05:02,190 --> 00:05:03,230
Ning Mochen,

76
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:06,620
this is the one last bad thing I'll do for you.

77
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:09,000
It is time to stop the whole thing.

78
00:05:14,910 --> 00:05:16,110
Let me guess.

79
00:05:18,820 --> 00:05:21,720
You're worried about losing to Su Yu, right?

80
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:27,950
Back then, Su Yu promised me

81
00:05:28,340 --> 00:05:29,670
that he'd stick with me.

82
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:32,280
But what happened when I woke up?

83
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:36,190
Men are fickle creatures.

84
00:05:37,790 --> 00:05:39,050
But I believe you can be

85
00:05:40,010 --> 00:05:41,409
as affectionate as he is.

86
00:05:43,790 --> 00:05:45,250
As long as we work as a team,

87
00:05:46,010 --> 00:05:47,940
we'll definitely get what we want.

88
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,460
Aren't you being too optimistic?

89
00:05:51,750 --> 00:05:54,640
Ningmei Jewelry is being impacted by negative press now.

90
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:57,720
It's true that some investors are selling off their shares,

91
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,360
but even if we buy them all,

92
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:00,760
we still can't

93
00:06:01,270 --> 00:06:02,670
drag Ning Zhaoxiong down

94
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:05,200
from the position of board president,

95
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:06,710
since we won't be holding enough shares.

96
00:06:06,710 --> 00:06:08,170
I'm certainly aware of it.

97
00:06:10,030 --> 00:06:11,710
That's why we need more allies.

98
00:06:11,710 --> 00:06:12,970
Who else would join us?

99
00:06:19,050 --> 00:06:20,660
Are you talking about Chen?

100
00:06:22,020 --> 00:06:23,220
Can't she be one of us?

101
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,110
Our plan hinges on

102
00:06:28,090 --> 00:06:30,280
the shares she's holding.

103
00:06:32,909 --> 00:06:34,800
You've got her into a miserable situation.

104
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,200
Now, you want her to be your ally

105
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,659
and to give you her shares.

106
00:06:37,890 --> 00:06:39,220
Do you think she'll agree to that?

107
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:40,659
It's just a pipe dream.

108
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,790
Everyone

109
00:06:46,030 --> 00:06:47,430
has a weak spot.

110
00:06:49,790 --> 00:06:51,190
I'll work out a solution.

111
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:56,690
Don't make a rash decision.

112
00:06:58,670 --> 00:06:59,670
I will

113
00:07:00,590 --> 00:07:01,590
talk to her first.

114
00:07:04,710 --> 00:07:06,640
I'll be waiting for your good news.

115
00:07:15,990 --> 00:07:16,710
Chen,

116
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:19,510
I didn't know you had moved in together.

117
00:07:20,540 --> 00:07:23,120
It's no wonder that you pretended not to know me last time.

118
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,520
He was the reason, right?

119
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:27,720
You said you wanted to tell me something important.

120
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,390
What is it?

121
00:07:29,130 --> 00:07:30,130
Here's the thing.

122
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:33,940
Previously, I've bought some shares of Ningmei stock.

123
00:07:34,670 --> 00:07:36,420
But if I am to have more power

124
00:07:36,630 --> 00:07:38,470
in the negotiation with Mr. Ning,

125
00:07:38,470 --> 00:07:39,800
I need a bit more shares.

126
00:07:41,190 --> 00:07:42,030
And so?

127
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:43,670
I want your shares.

128
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:45,510
Just name a price.

129
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:47,130
I want all your shares.

130
00:07:47,430 --> 00:07:48,560
Think of the payment

131
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:50,150
as an engagement present for you.

132
00:07:50,150 --> 00:07:51,720
Why do you want the shares

133
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:53,550
that Ning Mochen is holding?

134
00:07:53,710 --> 00:07:55,630
I want to be in charge of Ningmei Jewelry.

135
00:07:55,630 --> 00:07:57,950
So you're planning to force Ning Zhaoxiong out.

136
00:07:57,950 --> 00:07:58,880
For what reason?

137
00:08:00,510 --> 00:08:01,190
Chen,

138
00:08:02,170 --> 00:08:04,240
don't you always hate your father?

139
00:08:04,950 --> 00:08:06,550
You approached me in the past

140
00:08:06,670 --> 00:08:09,330
because you wanted to use me against him, right?

141
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:10,430
It's a pity

142
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:13,750
that you left me because I wasn't competent enough.

143
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:17,730
I hope your new boyfriend can be helpful to you.

144
00:08:21,430 --> 00:08:22,890
I'm not selling my shares.

145
00:08:23,910 --> 00:08:24,510
Why?

146
00:08:25,250 --> 00:08:26,870
I promise you won't suffer a loss.

147
00:08:26,870 --> 00:08:28,310
If you sell your shares now,

148
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:29,770
you'll earn a lot of money.

149
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:32,419
But once the stock price drops,

150
00:08:32,630 --> 00:08:33,650
you'll be stranded.

151
00:08:33,650 --> 00:08:35,600
When it happens, you'll lose everything.

152
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,799
I don't care of the price goes up or down.

153
00:08:37,870 --> 00:08:39,730
I'm not selling my shares anyway.

154
00:08:40,340 --> 00:08:42,340
You really need to think it through.

155
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:45,110
We're only one step away from success.

156
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:48,080
Your offer is declined.

157
00:08:51,570 --> 00:08:52,770
I guess today's visit

158
00:08:53,170 --> 00:08:54,430
is just a waste of time.

159
00:08:56,230 --> 00:08:56,950
Goodbye.

160
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:09,480
You've been involved

161
00:09:09,750 --> 00:09:11,190
with Zhao Lin and Yang Guang.

162
00:09:11,190 --> 00:09:12,310
How many more things

163
00:09:12,310 --> 00:09:13,640
are you keeping from me?

164
00:09:15,830 --> 00:09:16,670
Su Yu,

165
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:18,430
let's make a trade.

166
00:09:20,590 --> 00:09:21,710
From today on,

167
00:09:22,470 --> 00:09:25,270
I won't meet my ex-boyfriends anymore,

168
00:09:25,990 --> 00:09:28,320
and you won't spend time with Bai Li alone.

169
00:09:29,130 --> 00:09:30,930
These are two different things.

170
00:09:31,150 --> 00:09:33,810
None of your ex-boyfriends are good people, are they?

171
00:09:33,810 --> 00:09:35,000
Bai Li is different.

172
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:40,280
You have so much faith in Bai Li.

173
00:09:41,430 --> 00:09:42,110
It's great.

174
00:09:58,990 --> 00:09:59,710
Cha.

175
00:10:01,470 --> 00:10:02,390
Su Yu, you're here too.

176
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:03,990
Are you also visiting Bai Li?

177
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:07,770
But I'm not sure if I should get into the house.

178
00:10:08,630 --> 00:10:09,320
How so?

179
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:12,470
Last time I was here, Bai Li was very upset.

180
00:10:13,550 --> 00:10:15,500
She yelled at me and drove me away.

181
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:18,190
But you're Bai Li's best friend.

182
00:10:18,390 --> 00:10:19,650
You care a lot about her.

183
00:10:19,650 --> 00:10:21,060
Why would she do that?

184
00:10:22,270 --> 00:10:23,350
Maybe she was stressed out

185
00:10:23,350 --> 00:10:25,350
because she couldn't get her memories back.

186
00:10:25,350 --> 00:10:26,390
Or maybe

187
00:10:27,030 --> 00:10:29,160
Ning Mochen had some influence on her.

188
00:10:30,580 --> 00:10:32,710
I'm not trying to defend Ning Mochen,

189
00:10:32,710 --> 00:10:34,550
but the recent happenings

190
00:10:34,630 --> 00:10:37,270
have somewhat changed my opinion of her.

191
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:39,270
Indeed.

192
00:10:39,970 --> 00:10:41,790
The more time I spend with Ning Mochen,

193
00:10:41,790 --> 00:10:44,720
the more I feel she's different from my imagination.

194
00:10:44,830 --> 00:10:46,990
This incident has really taken a toll on her.

195
00:10:46,990 --> 00:10:50,590
Some terrible things she did long ago are revealed at this particular moment.

196
00:10:50,590 --> 00:10:51,830
It seems odd to me.

197
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:53,710
Yeah.

198
00:10:53,990 --> 00:10:56,920
There must be a ruse behind every unusual happening.

199
00:10:58,750 --> 00:11:01,810
But what kind of ruse can stop the truth from being true?

200
00:11:02,110 --> 00:11:02,830
Bai Li,

201
00:11:03,390 --> 00:11:04,230
you're back.

202
00:11:07,230 --> 00:11:08,890
A clean hand wants no washing.

203
00:11:09,030 --> 00:11:10,790
If she didn't do what she is accused of,

204
00:11:10,790 --> 00:11:12,520
the truth will come out one day.

205
00:11:13,270 --> 00:11:15,600
The cyber bullying will stop eventually.

206
00:11:16,590 --> 00:11:17,470
The two of you

207
00:11:17,950 --> 00:11:19,410
shouldn't worry too much.

208
00:11:20,030 --> 00:11:21,710
We were just chitchatting.

209
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:23,480
Go on with it.

210
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,020
Let's talk inside.

211
00:11:26,680 --> 00:11:28,010
You aren't mad at me now?

212
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:31,210
Why would I be mad at you?

213
00:11:31,630 --> 00:11:32,190
Let's go.

214
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:38,160
Come on in.

215
00:11:42,950 --> 00:11:43,750
Thank you.

216
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:50,910
Look, Bai Li,

217
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:52,280
you left the hospital not long ago.

218
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:54,020
It must be boring to stay at home alone.

219
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:55,310
When you were in college,

220
00:11:55,310 --> 00:11:56,830
you and Su Yu did design projects together.

221
00:11:56,830 --> 00:11:58,750
You were the best partner for each other.

222
00:11:58,750 --> 00:11:59,590
Why don't

223
00:11:59,590 --> 00:12:01,710
the two of you design a new series?

224
00:12:01,710 --> 00:12:02,970
I'm sure it'll be a hit.

225
00:12:05,270 --> 00:12:07,200
I haven't designed anything for a long time.

226
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,470
I'm a little rusty now.

227
00:12:09,090 --> 00:12:10,390
Even if I want to do that,

228
00:12:10,390 --> 00:12:12,350
I'm not sure if I'm capable of it.

229
00:12:12,700 --> 00:12:13,700
It's okay, Bai Li.

230
00:12:13,790 --> 00:12:14,710
After you reach a full recovery,

231
00:12:14,710 --> 00:12:16,150
you can try picking up the skills again.

232
00:12:16,150 --> 00:12:16,910
Don't worry.

233
00:12:16,930 --> 00:12:19,190
I'll help you find the old feelings back.

234
00:12:19,670 --> 00:12:20,470
No need.

235
00:12:20,490 --> 00:12:22,430
I have no inspiration for new designs now.

236
00:12:22,430 --> 00:12:24,230
Bai Li, you're very talented.

237
00:12:24,270 --> 00:12:24,790
Your talent is...

238
00:12:24,790 --> 00:12:26,650
I've told you I don't want to do it.

239
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,390
Sorry.

240
00:12:39,230 --> 00:12:40,500
Maybe...

241
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:43,940
Maybe because I can't recall anything

242
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:47,570
when you talk about the people and things in the past,

243
00:12:47,790 --> 00:12:49,070
I'm a bit stressed out.

244
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,150
Alright.

245
00:12:51,230 --> 00:12:52,760
Let's not talk about those.

246
00:12:59,110 --> 00:12:59,910
I'm sorry.

247
00:13:03,030 --> 00:13:04,760
You want my shares, right?

248
00:13:05,180 --> 00:13:06,130
Let's meet up.

249
00:13:13,490 --> 00:13:14,590
You guys keep talking.

250
00:13:14,590 --> 00:13:15,720
I need to take a call.

251
00:13:36,390 --> 00:13:37,520
Where shall we meet?

252
00:13:55,510 --> 00:13:57,640
Are you recording this conversation?

253
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:24,480
This time,

254
00:14:24,920 --> 00:14:26,450
try not to play dirty tricks

255
00:14:26,850 --> 00:14:28,250
like what you did before.

256
00:14:32,650 --> 00:14:35,200
I thought you were sent to a psychiatric hospital.

257
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:37,460
You would love to see that happen, right?

258
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:42,750
It's a surprise

259
00:14:43,270 --> 00:14:45,950
that you actually know your way around Su Yu.

260
00:14:46,830 --> 00:14:48,070
Even that big scandal

261
00:14:48,630 --> 00:14:50,220
didn't make him resent you.

262
00:14:50,990 --> 00:14:53,190
Instead, he let you move into his house.

263
00:14:56,110 --> 00:14:56,910
As I expected,

264
00:14:57,290 --> 00:14:59,150
it's you who sent Yang Guang over.

265
00:15:02,470 --> 00:15:04,910
Now that you have gotten to know everything,

266
00:15:04,910 --> 00:15:06,440
let's get down to business.

267
00:15:12,910 --> 00:15:13,550
Sign it.

268
00:15:19,890 --> 00:15:20,820
Ning Mochen,

269
00:15:21,950 --> 00:15:23,270
have you forgotten

270
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:25,810
how much suffering

271
00:15:25,950 --> 00:15:27,610
you've put me through lately?

272
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:29,730
In order to defeat Ning Zhaoxiong,

273
00:15:29,990 --> 00:15:32,700
you've even gone so far as to ruin your own reputation.

274
00:15:32,700 --> 00:15:35,430
You're determined to reach your goal at any cost.

275
00:15:37,150 --> 00:15:38,070
For me,

276
00:15:39,250 --> 00:15:41,210
reputation means nothing.

277
00:15:42,740 --> 00:15:43,870
What's more,

278
00:15:44,420 --> 00:15:46,550
someone else is taking the heat for me.

279
00:15:48,670 --> 00:15:49,720
As for you...

280
00:15:52,570 --> 00:15:54,700
Everything you have is supposed to be mine.

281
00:15:54,700 --> 00:15:57,700
Now, I'm just getting back what belongs to me.

